HEADWORD: Spate
<hw>Spate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Of Celtic origin; cf.
Ir. <ets>speid</ets>.]</ety> <def>A river flood; an overflow or
inundation.</def> <rj><au>Burns.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

